                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row" style="margin-top:150px; text-align:center; color:#192020">
                <div class="col-sm-7" style="margin-top:3%">
                    <h1>
                        Meme Driven Development
                    </h1>
                    <p>
                        The love of programming extends beyond what's useful and into the absurd. Suffice to say I've loved computers since I was a child. They are both serious and fun.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-offset-1 col-sm-4">
                    <a asp-action="ChilledESports" asp-controller="Home"><img style="height:200px; border:groove; border-radius:100px; border-color:darkgoldenrod;" src="~/images/shitposter.png" /></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
    <hr />
